thread.title: Maggie Guggenbiller Hudson
thread.title_full: Packlane reviewed by Maggie Guggenbiller Hudson

author: Maggie Guggenbiller Hudson
title: Maggie Guggenbiller Hudson
text: I had a great experience with Packlane. Service was quick, efficient and accurate and the boxes turned out beautifully! I was a little worried before they arrived because the prices and minimums are so reasonable but the quality was very high and the printing was excellent. We've had several people comment on the nice quality of the boxes and have been exceptionally happy with the end prodct.
